unmarshal

public Agent unmarshal(com.thoughtworks.xstream.io.HierarchicalStreamReader reader,
                       com.thoughtworks.xstream.converters.UnmarshallingContext context)
Reads an instance from XML. The belongings cannot be completely initialized, thus a later binding mechanism is required. World objects which model is null have to be replaced by the instances having the same ID. This mechanism is implemented in the EntitiesFactory.repairBelongings.

Specified by:

the read object or null if a problem arose.
